dct_description_sm: Lieuts. Norris & Weston & J. Mulheran & Assistants, Surveyors ; Published according to Act of Parliament by John Walker, Geographer to the Honble. East India Company August 15th, 1856 ; J. & C. Walker, Sculp.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Shows administrative divisions, roads, railways, towns, waterways
Includes area around Chandrapur ("Chanda" on map)
1856 version (and atlas index) available through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image.
